summary: A fix for HaileySkyrim\'s great Autumn Shire house.
descriptionHtml:
Just an .esp that fixes the broken bookshelves in Autumn Shire. I have not added or changed anything other than the bookshelves. Just replace the .esp and it should work fine. If there has been an update since the time of uploading, this fix is probably either unnecessary or not going to work.

--Hopefully this is just temporary until the mod is updated--

Requires the original mod:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30190
